column1: Dutton has already caught it once at a 5eyes meeting, while he was 'watching' spy movies of Julian Assange & his fiance in the bathroom. Come on Dutton, lets test the herd immunity theory. Go empty bed-pans for coronavirus patients.
'Australian intelligence officials' surely an oxymoron? They didn't have any intelligence on Coronavirus did they? 5eyes is just a domestic spying op. You show me mine & I'll show you yours.
